    <h3 itemprop="headline">Bikini-clad barista takes hammer to customer's windshield after he throws coffee at her</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      A viral video outside a bikini espresso shop in Seattle shows a wild confrontation involving a customer during which the owner smashed his windshield.
