    <h3 itemprop="headline">Kentuckians losing access to Pornhub</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Limiting or banning traffic in states is not new for Pornhub, which has blocked traffic in other states like Utah and Texas due to age verification laws.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/15/kentuckians-losing-access-to-pornhub/"  >(Dustin Massengill, WGN 9)</a>
    </p>
