    <h3 itemprop="headline">Candidates race to register for French election but one convicted of spousal assault withdraws</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      PARIS (AP) — Candidates were racing to register for an early parliamentary election before a Sunday evening deadline for a vote that's redrawing France's political landscape.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/16/candidates-race-to-register-for-french-election-but-one-convicted-of-spousal-assault-withdraws/"  >(Associated Press, PHL 17)</a>
    </p>
