           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Stress, depression linked to heart disease in women: Study</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Women under 50 with mental health issues are nearly twice as likely to develop cardiovascular risk factors.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/12/stress-depression-linked-to-heart-disease-in-women-study/"  >(Kelsey Kernstine, The Hill)</a>
    </p>
