           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Officials rescue 28 riders trapped upside-down at Portland amusement park</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      A ride at Oaks Amusement Park in Portland, Oregon, malfunctioned on Friday afternoon, trapping 28 people upside down, but no injuries were reported and all riders have since been evacuated and medically evaluated.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/15/officials-rescue-28-riders-trapped-upside-down-at-portland-amusement-park/"  >(Ariel Iacobazzi, KLAS, CBS News)</a>
