    <h3 itemprop="headline">OpenAI appoints former top US cyberwarrior Paul Nakasone to its board of directors</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      SAN FRANCISCO (AP) — OpenAI has appointed a former top U.S. cyberwarrior and intelligence official to its board of directors, saying he will help protect the ChatGPT maker from “increasingly sophisticated bad actors.” Retired Army Gen. Paul Nakasone was the commander of U.S.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/06/14/openai-appoints-former-top-us-cyberwarrior-paul-nakasone-to-its-board-of-directors/"  >(Associated Press, KRON4)</a>
    </p>
