    <h3 itemprop="headline">Why future Artemis astronauts need a better warning system on the moon</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      NASA has set its sights on the moon, aiming to send astronauts back to the lunar surface by 2026 and establish a long-term presence there by the 2030s. But the moon isn’t exactly a habitable place for people.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/06/15/moon-future-artemis-astronauts-better-warning-system/"  >(The Conversation, Fast Company)</a>
    </p>
