           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Massachusetts on verge of becoming second-to-last state to outlaw "revenge porn"</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      BOSTON (AP) — A bill aimed at outlawing “revenge porn” has been approved by lawmakers in the Massachusetts House and Senate and shipped to Democratic Gov. Maura Healey, a move advocates say was long overdue.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/06/13/massachusetts-on-verge-of-becoming-second-to-last-state-to-outlaw-revenge-porn/"  >(STEVE LeBLANC, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
