    <h3 itemprop="headline">Network jobs watch: Hiring, skills and certification trends</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Network and infrastructure roles continue to shift as enterprises adopt technologies such as AI-driven network operations, multicloud networking, zero trust network access (ZTNA), and SD-WAN.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/06/13/network-jobs-watch-hiring-skills-and-certification-trends/"  >(Network World)</a>
