    <h3 itemprop="headline">Power demand expected to double by 2040 thanks to AI and EVs, PG&#38;E&#8217;s CEO says</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      PG&#38;E is equipped to meet that surge in demand without significantly adding to its fleet of power plants, Chief Executive Officer Patti Poppe said. That’s because the utility’s system isn’t running at its full potential.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/06/14/power-demand-expected-to-double-by-2040-thanks-to-ai-and-evs-california-utility-says/"  >(Bloomberg, The Mercury News)</a>
