    <h3 itemprop="headline">Supersub Wout Weghorst scores late again in Netherlands' 2-1 win over Poland at Euro 2024</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      HAMBURG, Germany (AP) — Netherlands forward Wout Weghorst loves to make a big impression off the bench and he did it again Sunday late in a 2-1 win over Poland at the European Championship.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/06/16/supersub-wout-weghorst-scores-late-again-in-netherlands-2-1-win-over-poland-at-euro-2024/"  >(Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
