           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Jerry West, a 3-time Hall of Fame selection and the NBA logo, dies at 86</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      (AP) -- Jerry West, who was selected to the Basketball Hall of Fame three times in a storied career as a player and executive and whose silhouette is considered to be the basis of the NBA logo, died Wednesday morning, the Los Angeles Clippers announced. He was 86. West, nicknamed “Mr.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/06/12/jerry-west-a-3-time-hall-of-fame-selection-and-the-nba-logo-dies-at-86/"  >(The Associated Press, KRON4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 13 Jun 2024 03:30:10 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 13 Jun 2024 03:30:10 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Dana Greene, ABC 4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/sports/2024/06/13/jimmer-fredette-excited-to-play-in-the-olympics.webp" alt="Jimmer Fredette excited to play in the Olympics"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Jimmer Fredette excited to play in the Olympics</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      PROVO, Utah (ABC4 Sports) - Jimmer Fredette is an Olympic fanatic. "I love the Olympics," the former BYU star said. "Like, it's one of my favorite things. I watch every event and I have all the way up until now." Now, he gets to be a part of the Summer Games.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/06/13/jimmer-fredette-excited-to-play-in-the-olympics/"  >(Dana Greene, ABC 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
