           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Moose on the Loose: Remembering Jerry West</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      NEW YORK (PIX11) -- "The Logo." "Mr. Clutch." "Mr. Outside." "Zeke from Cabin Creek." There were many nicknames for Jerry West over his playing career. He was an icon. West passed away Wednesday at the age of 86.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/06/13/moose-on-the-loose-remembering-jerry-west/"  >(Marc Malusis, PIX 11)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
