    <p itemprop="text">
      LAS VEGAS (KLAS) -- Four votes separated the top two candidates in a North Las Vegas city council race as the county continued to tabulate primary results Wednesday. As of 1 p.m.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/06/12/tight-race-4-votes-separate-these-las-vegas-valley-candidates-after-nevada-primary-night/"  >(David Charns, KLAS, CBS News)</a>
