    <h3 itemprop="headline">Biden, Trump step up outreach to Black men</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      President Biden and former President Trump are ramping up their messaging toward Black male voters, underscoring the political power the demographic will hold in November.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/06/15/biden-trump-step-up-outreach-to-black-men/"  >(Cheyanne M. Daniels, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
