  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/politics/2024/06/14/minnesota-chippewa-tribe-general-elections-have-concluded-new-chairperson-to-lead-fond-du-lac.webp" alt="Minnesota Chippewa Tribe general elections have concluded, new chairperson to lead Fond du Lac Band"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Minnesota Chippewa Tribe general elections have concluded, new chairperson to lead Fond du Lac Band</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Several band’s incumbent candidates were reelected, while the Fond du Lac Band of Lake Superior Chippewa will have a change in leadership come July with a newly elected chairperson.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/06/14/minnesota-chippewa-tribe-general-elections-have-concluded-new-chairperson-to-lead-fond-du-lac/"  >(Melissa Olson, MPR News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 14 Jun 2024 04:15:21 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 14 Jun 2024 04:15:21 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Stephany Matat, Associated Press, KPRC 2">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/politics/2024/06/14/donald-trumps-78th-birthday-becomes-a-show-of-loyalty-for-his-fans-and-fellow-republicans.webp" alt="Trump marks his 78th birthday with a towering 'MAGA' cake and attacks on his 81-year-old rival's age"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Trump marks his 78th birthday with a towering 'MAGA' cake and attacks on his 81-year-old rival's age</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Donald Trump has marked his 78th birthday by addressing a fawning crowd in Florida, promising to crack down hard on the U.S.-Mexico border and repeatedly dismissing his opponent in November’s election, President Joe Biden, as too frail to handle a second term.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/06/14/donald-trumps-78th-birthday-becomes-a-show-of-loyalty-for-his-fans-and-fellow-republicans/"  >(Stephany Matat, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div></div></fieldset></main>
